… 앗…… 있다!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event16-02-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"히마리","body":"앗! 여보세요. 리사 선배~!\n이번 주말에 시간 괜찮으신가요?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event16-02-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"리사","body":"네, 여보세요…… 어라, 히마리잖아! 뭐야뭐야~?\n엇! 이번 주말? 응, 한가하긴 한데……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event16-02-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"리사","body":"바다~! 좋다~! 당연히 가지~!\n그럼 주말에 봐♪","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"event16-02-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"리사","body":"이야~ 바다라~! 몇 년 만이야~!\n……아, 뭐…… 분명 3년 만이었던가……","tention":0,"l